data.description: Introducing a beautiful 5-bedroom, two-story residence nestled in the Villages neighborhood. This home is a fusion of beauty & practicality. At the center of the home is a large kitchen, showcasing a generously sized island, an abundance of upgraded shaker cabinetry, smokey pearl granite countertops & spacious walk-in pantry. The versatile formal front room offers endless possibilities, whether it be a sophisticated sitting area, an office, or a dynamic flex space to suit your lifestyle. Located upstairs you will find all bedrooms, including an oversized Primary bedroom featuring an ensuite with separate tub & shower & two walk-in closets, & a separate full laundry room with ample storage space. Step outside onto the covered paver patio & low maintenance landscaping. Property also includes solar panels to ease the utility costs. With no rear neighbors & a walking trail beyond the rear of the property you have unobstructed views of the sunrise.
